{
  "stem": "8610.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, what does this word, 'chaplain,' mean?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, ugh, 'Er ist ein Vater.' He is a pastor, a sort of second-class quality to it-- [LAUGHS] second-class citizen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, fortunately, under attack of British guns we managed to escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a little experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, if that hadn't happened--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would have been a prisoner of war in a camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the tragedy was-- or the good thing was that when I go back to army headquarters [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and I reported about my experience, I managed to intercept the message which would have been sent back to my wife saying, 'missing presumed.' But I managed to-- and I wrote her-- sent her a cable saying, 'Escaped capture.' And she didn't realize what I meant.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyhow, that was an experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But fortunately, it was the Afrika Korps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were a much nicer set of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German officers I spoke to were-- I managed to speak to in English, without telling them that I understood German, they were really behaved very nicely.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the Afrika Korps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was Rommel, who wasn't a Hitlerite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was one experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could go on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it's-- that's really not the point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You want background, you've got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, having served abroad for three weeks-- three months-- three years, I was entitled to one week's leave per year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was given three weeks leave, during which time my chief said that he needed me to help out a certain place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I really had a couple of weeks free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I was posted overseas to Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By then, of course, we had invaded Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't get back into Europe until about late September 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
